data.description: Welcome Home to Your Serene Retreat overlooking the Winters Run Trail.  Nestled along the picturesque Winters Run Trail in Abingdon, MD, lies your perfect sanctuary. Just moments away from Singer Rd, with seamless access to routes 24 and 152, this end-of-group townhome offers not just a residence, but a lifestyle of tranquility and convenience.  As you step inside, natural light dances through windows on three sides, casting a warm glow upon the wood flooring and 9-foot ceilings that grace the main level. Your eyes are drawn to the beautifully updated kitchen, adorned with distressed white cabinetry, inviting you to explore your culinary passions.  Imagine mornings spent in the cozy family room, bathed in sunlight streaming through sliders that lead to your private deck, where the sounds of nature provide the perfect soundtrack to your day.  Ascending the stairs, you're greeted by the generous owner's suite, a haven of comfort and luxury. Cathedral ceilings soar overhead, creating a sense of space and grandeur. Picture evenings curled up by the two-sided fireplace, a novel in hand, or indulging in relaxation in the large bath, complete with a soaking tub, dual vanity, and separate shower.  The lower level beckons with promises of entertainment and relaxation. A spacious recreation room offers endless possibilities for gatherings with loved ones or quiet evenings in, while the fourth bedroom and third full bath provide flexibility and convenience for guests or family members.  But it's not just the features of this home that will capture your heart—it's the lifestyle it offers. Imagine strolling along the nearby Winters Run Trail, immersing yourself in the beauty of nature, or enjoying the ease of access to shopping, dining, and amenities just moments away.  This isn't just a house—it's a place where memories are made, where comfort and convenience come together to create the perfect retreat. Welcome home to Abingdon, where every day feels like a getaway.
